{"product_id":"madara-sos-hydra-repair-intensive-serum-30ml","title":"MÁDARA SOS Hydra Repair Intensive Serum 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eSOS Hydra Repair Intensive Serum works to restore moisture, balance and comfort, giving your skin a plumper look. The moisturising blend of Peony root, linseed and hyaluronic acid delivers immediate and long-lasting effects of hydrated, soothed and more luminous skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eApply to clean skin mornings and\/or evenings, follow with a moisturiser. For best results, use in combination with SOS Hydra Recharge Cream.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Pentylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Water, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Isoamyl Laurate, Cellulose, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Extract, Sodium PCA, Aroma, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Hyaluronate, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Seed Extract, Paeonia Lactiflora (Peony) Root Extract, Tocopherol, Urtica Dioica (Nettle) Leaf Extract, Mica (CI 77019), CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Aqua, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Sodium phytate, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), Benzyl Alcohol, Potassium Hydroxide, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol, Geraniol, Benzyl Salicylate, Eugenol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49858992177479,"sku":null,"price":37.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-hydra-repair-intensive-serum-30ml-456327.jpg?v=1739897256","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-sos-hydra-repair-intensive-serum-30ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}